- **Single model test**: ~$0.02-0.05 per video
- **Comparison test**: ~$0.04-0.10 (generates 2 videos)
- **Use**: `--hailuo` or `--kling` for single model testing

### Avatar Generation Costs  
- **Single voice test**: ~$0.03-0.05 per avatar video
